      <title>瑞士央行研究详细说明需要数十亿美元来控制货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/snb-research-details-billions-needed-to-keep-currency-in-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份工作人员文件显示，瑞士央行需要花费大约 270 亿法郎（300 亿美元）来阻止其货币升值 1.1%，该文件罕见地揭示了官员们的想法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/snb-research-details-billions-needed-to-keep-currency-in-check</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:30:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴尔的摩港船舶交通转移至东海岸港口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/baltimore-harbor-ship-traffic-moves-to-east-coast-ports-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国东海岸港口正在调整其运营方式，以吸收从巴尔的摩港转移的货物，在那里打捞专家开始清除被毁坏的弗朗西斯·斯科特基桥上的碎片。彭博资讯的 Lee Klaskow 在彭博电视上解释了货物如何重新分配到其他港口。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/baltimore-harbor-ship-traffic-moves-to-east-coast-ports-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:07:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告警告称，今年美国家庭保险保费可能创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-home-insurance-premiums-may-hit-a-record-this-year-report-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年美国房主保险的平均保费预计将达到 2,522 美元，比 2023 年底增长 6%。佛罗里达州的保费将接近 12,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/us-home-insurance-premiums-may-hit-a-record-this-year-report-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 12:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RBC 的 Calvasina 将标准普尔 500 指数目标上调至 5,300 点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/rbc-s-calvasina-boosts-s-p-500-target-to-5-300-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行资本市场 (RBC Capital Markets) 美国股票策略主管洛里·卡尔瓦西纳 (Lori Calvasina) 表示，在解释提高标准普尔 500 指数目标背后的因素时，市场轮动已经开始发生。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/rbc-s-calvasina-boosts-s-p-500-target-to-5-300-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 11:14:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安给土耳其经济计划更多时间，里拉飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/lira-dips-after-turkey-opposition-parties-sweep-local-elections-lugi5xc7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其里拉扭转了早些时候的跌势，周一兑美元汇率飙升，总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安表示，尽管周末地方选举面临前所未有的溃败，但他将给他的经济团队更多时间来取得成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/lira-dips-after-turkey-opposition-parties-sweep-local-elections-lugi5xc7</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 05:21:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受青睐的美联储通胀指标推动金价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/gold-xauusd-hits-record-on-fed-cut-outlook-and-geopolitical-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于有迹象表明美联储即将降息，金价升至历史新高，这也为金价上涨提供了动力，而金价上涨也是由地缘政治紧张局势和强劲的中国需求推动的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/gold-xauusd-hits-record-on-fed-cut-outlook-and-geopolitical-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 00:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
